  <a name="annual-fund"></a>
  



      <div id="mmi-23295" class="scrolling-text-module colspan-4 rag measurable magic-module" data-event-category="magic_module/scrolling_text_module/23295" data-event-label="Scrolling Text Module Annual Fund (4/11)" data-instance-id="23295" data-id="108522">                  <div class="scrolling-text-module__inner" style="max-height: 62.4em" tabindex="0">
    <h4 class="scrolling-text-module__title page-title--prominence-4">Annual Fund</h4>
    <p>Gifts from alumni, parents, friends, and anyone interested in art make an immediate impact on the School. Scholarship funds are the top priority and the money received from Annual Fund donations directly supports our students. Gifts of all sizes make an impact.</p>

<p><strong><font size="6"><a href="https://secure.yale.imodules.com/s/1667/52/cart/form.aspx?sid=1667&amp;gid=52&amp;pgid=5594&amp;cid=14277&amp;bledit=1&amp;dids=70.71.557.742.739.740.741.&amp;origin=5767&amp;_ga=2.222706072.26127765.1750777443-2035703091.1741025936" target="_blank">Give now</a></font></strong></p>

</div>

